content: Can someone help me with the link for text training and sending messages to voters?  I am struggling to navigate discord.
Hi John. I'm going to send a couple links to help you out!

Here's a great intro for how to use this discord server by our Community Mod Carolyn:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cA32MMsN61g

And here are the training times for Text Team:

https://events.democrats.org/event/672393/

Also, you can get oriented to the server at <#1268398483841220649> and <#1268398608097476750> which show a suggested workflow for your time here. Once you complete a text team training it can take up to a day or two to be added to the team. In the meantime, you can peruse our other channels, try out other team trainings, and chat with us in <#1242249109298221069> or ask any questions that come up there!
